Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也是來探病的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.75,0:01:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:01:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.25,0:02:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是不想待在辦公室裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛田 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.82,0:02:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次見到紅老師可別再暈倒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就別提這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.45,0:02:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次 看鳴人的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.75,0:02:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她完全暈倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著渾身是傷的鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.65,0:02:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.05,0:02:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算找到你了 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.84,0:02:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手婆婆 我有話和你說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.45,0:02:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 和鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛田 雛田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離這麼近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.75,0:02:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像臉色非常紅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有發燒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:03:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛田 不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點 雛田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.15,0:03:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連赤丸也嫉妒的超追蹤力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋找夢幻的微香蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是綱手大人親自審問
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水木還是什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.45,0:03:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在能夠找到大蛇丸的線索已經完全…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果他也是大蛇丸的棄子之一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不知道佐助的去向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和水木拼命戰鬥 結果卻是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人無法接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說綱手婆婆 沒關係的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說不行就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:03:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人現在也無法專心工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人一直都纏著她 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能批准他去找佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就偷偷溜出了辦公室…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果中了埋伏 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說好幾遍了 讓我去找佐助吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.75,0:04:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也說好幾遍了 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是要修煉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色仙人不在 修煉不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸也好 佐助也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有他們的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎麼找
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總會有辦法的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有消息的話 我會去打聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個不明事理的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手婆婆也是個不明事理的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 不錯 寧次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏要再往前半步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下吧 寧次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也喝點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛田既然來了 也該多看會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛田大小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是看看 也是一種修煉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開飯了 開飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才幹得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經接近完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了兩位的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天陪我來這裏特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是一個小隊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊裏的同伴有困難的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們當然會出手幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是理所當然的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:07:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有一個同伴突然失蹤的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定非常痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說鳴人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能幫幫他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然想幫他做點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人也對鳴人說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有線索
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦法倒是有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微香蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微香蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是被稱為夢幻之蟲的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說很早以前就已經絕種了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為怕他絕種
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.35,0:07:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們油女一族也停止使用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 應該還有少數存活在某個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人 那個微香蟲是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也難怪你不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一次使用微香蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也距離上次大戰很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微香蟲是蟲使所用蟲的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.45,0:08:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從卵裏出生的幼蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一會兒就成了蛹 然後化羽成蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後讓它們去辨認氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使很微弱也能找到這股味道的來源
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們的嗅覺是忍犬的幾千倍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有著超強的尋人能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過微香蟲好像幾年才產一次卵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年正好是產卵之年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且現在正好也是孵化的時期
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子裏還有佐助留下的東西 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果讓微香蟲聞這個氣味的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能知道佐助的所在地了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠找到微香蟲的概率是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說並不高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計有10%的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10%
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也應該知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在村子正處於非常困難的時期
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是下忍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能隨便地自由行動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞翁失馬焉知非福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為紅進了醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也基本沒任務可執行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其閑著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不如去賭一賭這10%的概率
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,油女志乃 犬塚牙 日向雛田
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在命令你們去尋找微香蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次由志乃指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.85,0:09:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 那邊的老鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.15,0:10:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不讓你去也不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來只有讓你去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.95,0:10:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這可是最後的機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果找不到微香蟲的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就對佐助的事死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 一定會找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 可別食言哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個得意忘形的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.25,0:10:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.25,0:10:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧次馬上就要過來修煉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶點就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下要去執行任務
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別拖大家的後腿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.25,0:11:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個大轉身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛田大小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊 雛田
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那麼就出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼走這麼慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以忍者的速度走到微香蟲的棲息地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要兩天左右的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要一開始就這麼著急
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在我們到之前卵就孵化了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微香蟲的卵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在雨後的第二天早晨才會孵化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時還不會下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 可是 萬一…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本隊的隊長是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務中請聽隊長的指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.65,0:12:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難想像你至今是怎麼和那個傢伙相處的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:12:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會和鳴人成為好朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人他們剛才出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.45,0:13:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋找蟲子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志乃最合適不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還有擁有白眼的雛田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及嗅覺超群的牙和赤丸同行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.55,0:13:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒必要再去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.55,0:13:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下我的任務就是儘快成為醫療忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天快黑了 搭帳篷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:13:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經搭帳篷了嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一點兒都不累呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再往前走點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 本隊的隊長是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經睡覺了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多數動植物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日落則眠 日出則醒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要尋找蟲的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必須親身去體會它們的生活節奏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 太陽才剛落山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 本隊的隊長是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是 我知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼早怎麼可能睡得著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖這麼說 竟然這麼快就睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓噓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瀑布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 嚇到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.05,0:16:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡了這麼久 還沒睡夠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上起來小便
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.87,0:16:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到一件不得了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛田也感冒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼個不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瀑布裏有個非常漂亮的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人揮手的同時 水也舞動了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上去打招呼時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.15,0:17:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會是做夢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像也這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.95,0:17:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛田的臉非常紅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會真感冒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個果實可以吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就吃它了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也能節約我們的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一點要注意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一種人型大的果實
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了會狂瀉不止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬不要碰它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有哪個傻瓜會吃那麼大的傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.45,0:18:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 要出發了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬…上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:19:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了 就是這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是第一次看到這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不像人能生活的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以對蟲子們來說就是樂園了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.75,0:19:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道那裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有微香蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個比中忍考試簡單多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 太脆了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.92,0:19:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為隊長我有一個警告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候 什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事不說我也知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.65,0:20:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要警告你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務完成之後 一定要好好揍你一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就是微香蟲之森
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 是木葉的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這裏的話 說明他們的目的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 和我們一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微香蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們絕不會把微香蟲讓給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:21:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微香蟲是我們上水流一族的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.89,0:22:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個照片的蟲子我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.71,0:22:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.65,0:22:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 沒想到這就是微香蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里見到的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上在廚房裏偷偷摸摸的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是便用拖鞋…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.38,0:22:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.23,0:22:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.15,0:22:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的只不過是普通的蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.09,0:22:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.93,0:23:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里不對了 蟲子怎麼看都一樣
